## Goals

- Clear module boundaries
- Predictable dependency direction
- Testable domain and application layers
- Safe evolution without big-bang rewrites

## Recommended layout

```
src/
  modules/          # feature modules (or domain/application/infrastructure)
  shared/           # shared kernel utilities
  providers/        # composition / DI wiring
```

## Dependency rules

1. Domain must not depend on frameworks or infrastructure
2. Application orchestrates use cases
3. Infrastructure implements ports/adapters
4. Presentation depends inward only

